metadata.name: Cloudies #2
metadata.description:
Cloudies have been here for all of eternity, looking down on the mortal realms and allowing the mortal beings to do as they please.

Enough is enough, the Cloudies have made themselves known as the Gods of the mortal realms. No longer will they stand by and watch. They are here to prove they are simply superior to all those beneath them. 

When you look to the skies, we will be looking back.
